  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The overall aim of the study is an early asthma diagnosis in young children by the use of
      non-invasive biomarkers of airway inflammation /oxidative stress in exhaled air, and early
      lung function measurements
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
